244
00:16:46,036 --> 00:16:47,733
- You try it.
- Okay.

245
00:16:54,317 --> 00:16:56,085
All right!

246
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:59,984
No. He already knows
that he owns everything in the room.

247
00:17:00,197 --> 00:17:02,770
He's not finding it
out for the first time.

248
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:05,483
- So try it again.
- Okay.

249
00:17:12,582 --> 00:17:15,156
He's not angry at the room either.

250
00:17:16,583 --> 00:17:19,537
Try it again. He owns it.
He owns the room.

251
00:17:19,784 --> 00:17:24,375
It is his. He owns, owns,
owns the room! He owns it!

252
00:17:25,107 --> 00:17:27,290
It's a little weird,
but it's getting better.

253
00:17:29,456 --> 00:17:33,561
I'm gonna miss this woman so much.
I don't know what I'm gonna do.

254
00:17:33,875 --> 00:17:36,058
It's been 20 years of my life.

255
00:17:36,589 --> 00:17:40,029
Hey, hey. Maybe this is a good thing.

256
00:17:40,347 --> 00:17:44,237
It'll give you a chance to shake
things up. Play different characters.

257
00:17:44,556 --> 00:17:45,872
You're so talented.

258
00:17:46,087 --> 00:17:48,483
