259
00:17:48,697 --> 00:17:50,357
But I don't know. You know...

260
00:17:50,576 --> 00:17:55,024
...an actor of a certain age,
it's not that easy.

261
00:17:55,272 --> 00:18:00,907
That's not true. Look at Angela
Lansbur... Angelina Jolie.

262
00:18:03,379 --> 00:18:08,029
